            "pair_id": "pair-001",
            "annotator": "Captain Curator",
            "html": "<div style=\"max-width:1100px; margin:0 auto; padding:16px; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial; color:#111827; line-height:1.5;\">\n  <!-- Responsive 1\u20132 column grid without external CSS -->\n  <div id=\"pair-grid\" style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:16px;\">\n    <section style=\"position:relative; background:#ffffff; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:14px; padding:20px; box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);\">\n    <div style=\"position:absolute; top:-14px; left:-14px; height:40px; width:40px; border-radius:9999px; background:#111827; color:#ffffff; display:grid; place-items:center; font-weight:600;\">\n      A\n    </div>\n\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc; padding-left:22px; margin:0;\">\n      <li><span style=\"font-weight:600;\">Name:</span> trimal</li>\n\n      <li><span style=\"font-weight:600;\">Source:</span> biotools, galaxy_metadata, toolshed, bioconda_recipes</li><li><span style=\"font-weight:600;\">Version:</span> 1.4, 0.1.0, 2.0-RC, 1.4.1</li><li><span style=\"font-weight:600;\">Labels:</span> trimal, trimAl: a tool for automated alignment trimming, trimAl</li><li>\n          <span style=\"font-weight:600;\">Web:</span>\n          <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc; padding-left:22px; margin:6px 0 0 0;\">\n            <li><a href=\"http://trimal.cgenomics.org/\" style=\"color:#2563eb; text-decoration:none;\">http://trimal.cgenomics.org/</a></li><li><a href=\"https://trimal.readthedocs.io/\" style=\"color:#2563eb; text-decoration:none;\">https://trimal.readthedocs.io/</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </li><li>\n          <span style=\"font-weight:600;\">Repository:</span>\n          <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc; padding-left:22px; margin:6px 0 0 0;\"><li>\n            <a href=\"https://github.com/scapella/trimal\" style=\"color:#2563eb; text-decoration:none;\">https://github.com/scapella/trimal</a> <span style=\"font-size:12px; color:#374151;\">(github)</span></li><li>\n            <a href=\"https://github.com/inab/trimal\" style=\"color:#2563eb; text-decoration:none;\">https://github.com/inab/trimal</a> <span style=\"font-size:12px; color:#374151;\">(github)</span></li></ul>\n        </li><li>\n          <span style=\"font-weight:600;\">Download:</span>\n          <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc; padding-left:22px; margin:6px 0 0 0;\">\n            <li><a href=\"https://github.com/scapella/trimal/archive/v1.4.1.tar.gz\" style=\"color:#2563eb; text-decoration:none;\">https://github.com/scapella/trimal/archive/v1.4.1.tar.gz</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </li><li>\n          <span style=\"font-weight:600;\">Documentation:</span>\n          <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc; padding-left:22px; margin:6px 0 0 0;\"><li><span style=\"font-weight:600;\">\n                Installation Instructions\n              </span>:\n              <a href=\"https://bioconda.github.io/recipes/trimal/README.html\" style=\"color:#2563eb; text-decoration:none;\">\n                https://bioconda.github.io/recipes/trimal/README.html\n              </a></li><li><span style=\"font-weight:600;\">\n                General\n              </span>:\n              <a href=\"https://bioconda.github.io/recipes/trimal/README.html\" style=\"color:#2563eb; text-decoration:none;\">\n                https://bioconda.github.io/recipes/trimal/README.html\n              </a></li><li><span style=\"font-weight:600;\">\n                General\n              </span>:\n              <a href=\"https://trimal.readthedocs.io/\" style=\"color:#2563eb; text-decoration:none;\">\n                https://trimal.readthedocs.io/\n              </a></li></ul>\n        </li><li><span style=\"font-weight:600;\">Authors:</span> <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc; padding-left:22px; margin:6px 0 0 0;\"><li>\n          Salvador Capella-Gutierrez (Person, salcagu@gmail.com)\n        </li><li>\n          Unknown (Person, tgabaldon@crg.es)\n        </li></ul></li><li><span style=\"font-weight:600;\">OS:</span> Windows, macOS, Linux</li><li>\n          <span style=\"font-weight:600;\">License:</span>\n          <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc; padding-left:22px; margin:6px 0 0 0;\"><li>\n                GPL-3.0-or-later \u2014 <a href=\"https://spdx.org/licenses/GPL-3.0-or-later.html\" style=\"color:#2563eb; text-decoration:none;\">https://spdx.org/licenses/GPL-3.0-or-later.html</a></li></ul>\n        </li><li>\n          <span style=\"font-weight:600;\">Description:</span>\n          <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc; padding-left:22px; margin:6px 0 0 0;\">\n            <li>A tool for the automated removal of spurious sequences or poorly aligned regions from a multiple sequence alignment.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </li></ul>\n  </section>\n    <section style=\"position:relative; background:#ffffff; border:1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius:14px; padding:20px; box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);\">\n    <div style=\"position:absolute; top:-14px; left:-14px; height:40px; width:40px; border-radius:9999px; background:#111827; color:#ffffff; display:grid; place-items:center; font-weight:600;\">\n      B\n    </div>\n\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc; padding-left:22px; margin:0;\">\n      <li><span style=\"font-weight:600;\">Name:</span> trimal</li>\n\n      <li><span style=\"font-weight:600;\">Source:</span> sourceforge</li><li><span style=\"font-weight:600;\">Labels:</span> trimal</li><li>\n          <span style=\"font-weight:600;\">Web:</span>\n          <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc; padding-left:22px; margin:6px 0 0 0;\">\n            <li><a href=\"https://trimal.sourceforge.io/\" style=\"color:#2563eb; text-decoration:none;\">https://trimal.sourceforge.io/</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </li><li>\n          <span style=\"font-weight:600;\">Repository:</span>\n          <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc; padding-left:22px; margin:6px 0 0 0;\"><li>\n            <a href=\"https://sourceforge.net/projects/trimal\" style=\"color:#2563eb; text-decoration:none;\">https://sourceforge.net/projects/trimal</a> <span style=\"font-size:12px; color:#374151;\">(sourceforge)</span></li></ul>\n        </li><li>\n          <span style=\"font-weight:600;\">Download:</span>\n          <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc; padding-left:22px; margin:6px 0 0 0;\">\n            <li><a href=\"https://sourceforge.net/projects/trimal\" style=\"color:#2563eb; text-decoration:none;\">https://sourceforge.net/projects/trimal</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </li><li><span style=\"font-weight:600;\">OS:</span> Linux, Windows</li><li>\n          <span style=\"font-weight:600;\">Description:</span>\n          <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc; padding-left:22px; margin:6px 0 0 0;\">\n            <li>TrimAl is a bioinformatic tool that cleans multiple protein or nucleotide sequence alignment. The clean alignment (as a result of the TrimAl cleaning process) is used for phylogenetic reconstruction. TrimAl improves the quality of the reconstructed trees.</li>\n          </ul>\n        </li></ul>\n  </section>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Optional small inline script to switch to 2 columns \u2265900px -->\n  <script>\n    (function () {\n      var grid = document.getElementById('pair-grid');\n      function setCols() {\n        if (window.innerWidth >= 900) {\n          grid.style.gridTemplateColumns = '1fr 1fr';\n        } else {\n          grid.style.gridTemplateColumns = '1fr';\n        }\n      }\n      setCols();\n      window.addEventListener('resize', setCols);\n    })();\n  </script>\n</div>"
    }
}